Uttar Pradesh
Nov 24, 2014
Abuse
Description:
			A woman was brutally beaten up and left injured by her husband at bus stand here last evening, police said today.

Ladpura resident Harbir had married off his daughter Rajni to Delhi resident Amit eight years ago.

Amit used to regularly physically and mentally torture her. Yesterday Amit had beaten up Rajni and left her injured at Ladpura village bus stand, police said.

The victim's brother Mohit lodged an FIR at Greater Noida police station against Amit, father-in-law Balraj and others, police said, adding that the victim's condition was stable.


